[38;5;129m│[0m Keep-Alive\r\ncontent-type: text/plain\r\n\r\n=== Canto ===\r\nContributors: [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m Canto Inc, ianthekid, flightjim\r\nTags: digital asset management, brand     [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m management, cloud storage, DAM, file storage, image management, photo        [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m library, Canto\r\nRequires at least: 5.0\r\nTested up to: 6.1\r\nStable tag: [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m 3.0.4\r\nLicense: GPLv2 or later\r\nLicense URI:                             [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html\r\n\r\nEasily find and publish your [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m creative assets directly to wordpress without having to search through       [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m emails or folders, using digital asset management by Canto.\r\n\r\n==        [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m Description ==\r\n\r\nSimplify collaboration with your creative team by      [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m publishing photos, images, and other web-safe media from Canto directly to   [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m your WordPress website.\r\nInstead of sending files back and forth, browse   [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m or search your Canto library directly in WordPress. You can search for text  [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m within file names, descriptions, comments, keywords, tags, or even the name  [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m of the person who uploaded the file to Canto.\r\nOnce you click to insert    [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m the image, it will save automatically to your WordPress Media                [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m Library.\r\nDon’t have a Canto account? <a                                   [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m href="https://www.canto.com/signup/?utm_source=wordpress&utm_medium=plugin&u [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m tm_campaign=wordpress">Start a free trial</a> today!\r\n\r\n== Installation  [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m ==\r\n\r\nInstalling Canto wordpress plugin can be done either by searching  [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m for "Canto" via the "Plugins > Add New" screen in your WordPress dashboard,  [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m or by using the following steps:\r\n\r\n1. Download the plugin via           [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m WordPress.org\r\n2. Upload the ZIP file through the \'Plugins > Add New >    [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m Upload\' screen in your WordPress dashboard\r\n3. Activate the plugin        [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m through the \'Plugins\' menu in WordPress\r\n\r\nConfigure and authorize     [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m your account under "Settings > Canto" left nav menu. Click "Connect" and     [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m enter in your account credentials. You will be automatically redirected back [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m to WordPress.\r\n\r\nAll set, enjoy!\r\n\r\n== Screenshots ==\r\n\r\n1. Find [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m media assets quickly with Canto digital asset management\r\n2. Insert into   [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m Post directly from our CDN\r\n3. Inserts a native Gutenberg block with       [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m customizable options and formatting\r\n4. Canto block under Common           [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m Blocks\r\n5. Plugin settings include duplicate checking and automatic        [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m updates for assets imported in WordPress\r\n\r\n== Frequently Asked          [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m Questions ==\r\n\r\n= Canto Help =\r\n\r\nFor help installing or using the   [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m plugin, refer to <a href="https://cantodam.freshdesk.com/">Canto             [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m Help</a>\r\n\r\n= Can I use this plugin without a Canto account?             [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m =\r\n\r\nUnfortunately not. However, you are welcome to sign up today for    [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m free! <a                                                                     [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m href="https://www.canto.com/signup/?utm_source=wordpress&utm_medium=plugin&u [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m tm_campaign=wordpress">Start free trial</a>\r\n\r\n= How do I authorize my   [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m account? =\r\n\r\nWe recommend you to connect to your Canto account using an [38;5;129m│[0m
